Don feels like he is a hero and he has to save world from monsters. But thats not really true. He forced Sancho to go with him on multiple adventuresn by making false promises to him. 
On the first day, they go to a farm with windmills. Don feels that those windmills are giants and they are waving their hands at him.So he goes to attack the windmills and realizes that they are not giants but windmills. Shocked by that he tells Sancho that wizard did a trick. The wizard converted giants into windmills.
Sancho thought that Don has gone mad finally.
